        "version_name": "和合本新標點（神版）",
        "lang": "cht",
        "text": "是萬軍之耶和華所定的！ 為要污辱一切高傲的榮耀， 使地上一切的尊貴人被藐視。"
      },
      "nasb": {
        "version_id": "NASB",
        "version_name": "New American Standard Bible",
        "lang": "en",
        "text": "The Lord of hosts has planned it, to defile the pride of all beauty, To despise all the honored of the earth."
      },
